==性质==
1、亚硝酸酯的[[冰醋酸|冰醋酸]]溶液中存在[[乙酰硝酸酯|乙酰硝酸酯]]（CH<sub>3</sub>COONO<sub>2</sub>），乙酰硝酸酯是温和的[[硝化剂|硝化试剂]]，可对其他化合物进行硝化，它也存在于较为传统的[[硝酸|硝酸]]-[[乙酸酐|乙酸酐]]硝化系统中。

2、[[亚硝酸正丁酯|亚硝酸正丁酯]]和[[氨|氨]]可将[[苯基羟胺|苯基羟胺]]转化为其''N''-[[亚硝基|亚硝基]]衍生物[[铜铁试剂|铜铁试剂]]。<ref>C. S. Marvel. "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv1p0177 Cupferron] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv1p0177 |date=20120205193848 }}". ''[[有机合成_(期刊)|Org. Synth.]]''; ''Coll. Vol. '''1''''': 177. (1941); ''Coll. Vol. '''4''''': 19. (1925).</ref>[[吡咯烷|吡咯烷]]也可与[[亚硝酸乙酯|亚硝酸乙酯]]生成相应的''N''-NO衍生物。<ref>D. Enders, R. Pieter, B. Renger, and D. Seebach. "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV6P0542.pdf Nucleophilic α-sec-Aminoalkylation: 2-(Diphenylhydroxymethyl)pyrrolidine] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV6P0542.pdf |date=20071010060132 }}". ''[[有机合成_(期刊)|Org. Synth.]]''; ''Coll. Vol. '''6''''': 542. (1988); ''Coll. Vol. '''58''''': 113. (1978).</ref>

3、在酸或碱催化下，亚硝酸酯可与較強的[[碳负离子|碳负离子]]反应，在α位引入[[肟|肟]]基（＝NOH）。例如，用[[丁酮|丁酮]]、[[亚硝酸乙酯|亚硝酸乙酯]]、[[盐酸|盐酸]]反应，然后用[[羟胺磺酸钠|羟胺磺酸钠]]处理，则最后可以得到[[丁二酮肟|丁二酮肟]]；<ref>W. L. Semon, V. R. Damerell. "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV2P0204.pdf Dimethylglyoxime] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV2P0204.pdf |date=20070926232530 }}". ''[[有机合成_(期刊)|Org. Synth.]]''; ''Coll. Vol. '''2''''': 204. (1943); ''Coll. Vol. '''10''''': 22. (1930).</ref>如果以[[苯酰甲基氯|苯酰甲基氯]]为原料，亚硝酸正丁酯为试剂，在酸性条件下反应，则可得ω-氯肟基苯乙酮；<ref>Nathan Levin, Walter H. Hartung. "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV3P0191.pdf ω-Chloroisonitrosoacetophenone] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV3P0191.pdf |date=20071010060807 }}". ''[[有机合成_(期刊)|Org. Synth.]]''; ''Coll. Vol. '''3''''': 191. (1955); ''Coll. Vol. '''24''''': 25. (1944).</ref>用亚硝酸甲酯在[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]中处理[[苯乙腈|苯乙腈]]，则可得α-肟基苯乙腈。<ref>Masumi Itoh, Daijiro Hagiwara, Takashi Kamiya1. "[http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV6P0199.pdf A New Reagent for tert-Butoxycarbonylation: 2-tert-Butoxycarbonyloxyimino-2-phenylacetonitrile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV6P0199.pdf |date=20071008034821 }}". ''[[有机合成_(期刊)|Org. Synth.]]''; ''Coll. Vol. '''6''''': 199. (1988); ''Coll. Vol. '''59''''': 95. (1979).</ref>

